{"tid":1271334,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【引渡惡法】警方要求遊行延期 民陣拒絕","createTime":"2019-07-01T06:09:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T06:55:29.000Z","uid":50457,"like":47,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9422267202766ea3e951fb13a309a91ded65a5ab","tid":1271334,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T06:09:16.000Z","msg":"點<br />\n<br />\n全部<br />\n<br />\n要聞<br />\n<br />\n突發<br />\n<br />\n娛樂<br />\n<br />\n兩岸<br />\n<br />\n國際<br />\n<br />\n財經<br />\n<br />\n果籽<br />\n<br />\n飲食男女<br />\n<br />\n體育<br />\n<br />\n賽馬<br />\n<br />\n影片推介<br />\n<br />\nKetchuper<br />\n<br />\n主頁<br />\n<br />\n即時<br />\n<br />\n動新聞<br />\n<br />\n日報<br />\n<br />\n果燃台<br />\n<br />\n即時分類<br />\n<br />\n焦點<br />\n<br />\n全部<br />\n<br />\n要聞<br />\n<br />\n突發<br />\n<br />\n娛樂<br />\n<br />\n兩岸<br />\n<br />\n國際<br />\n<br />\n財經<br />\n<br />\n果籽<br />\n<br />\n飲食男女<br />\n<br />\n體育<br />\n<br />\n賽馬<br />\n<br />\n影片推介<br />\n<br />\nKetchuper<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n【引渡惡法】警方要求遊行延期 民陣拒絕<br />\n<br />\n12分鐘前<br />\n<br />\n即時突發<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n警方指民陣拒絕延期建議。文兆麟攝<br />\n<br />\n港島總區總部（行動部）總督察古兆輝，對於立法會有示威者正進行暴力衝擊，對警方及公眾構成極大安全威脅，警方予以最嚴厲的譴責，並會嚴肅跟進並調查。<br />\n<br />\n另外，古兆輝指，今日凌晨4時，大批示威者衝出龍和道一帶，並以物件阻塞交通，又在附近地盤撿磚塊，運到灣仔會展。至早上7時左右，示威者開始衝擊警方，因此警方作出驅散行動。<br />\n其間，示威者擲出不明物體，令警員受傷，包括呼吸困難及皮膚紅腫。該13人經治理後，已經全部出院。警方對於示威者連串的行為，予以強烈譴責。<br />\n<br />\n鑑於現場帶有暴力的示威者有約1,500人，警方與主辦單位聯絡，並建議他們延期舉行或維持在維園內舉行，但均遭到拒絕。警方指，主辦單位有責任保障參與者人士的安全，因此市民亦要慎重考慮是否參加。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190701/59776442\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190701%2F59776442&d=IJ4Nzxd4hLWYFZk0XL5PgTMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=bcd4e3c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190701%2F59776442&h=0af9a70d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190701/59776442</a>"},{"pid":"9eabb7ea8e9c63e9fc7507ba76a2e109ebf62dc4","tid":1271334,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T06:09:58.000Z","msg":"［向三毛五毛學習，分化藍絲第三集］每次活動後鼓吹失敗主義，用活動手法差異分化群眾，零晨留言引人互屌<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1271316\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1271316</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7788293c214a1f6b2f31139f21ba642e4e192fa9","tid":1271334,"uid":6435,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T06:10:10.000Z","msg":"真係想CUT 71<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8afe7b11c462ad56e0949d2fd4b593dbf9a0a34","tid":1271334,"uid":50457,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T06:10:51.000Z","msg":"遊行人士一到，警察就增援唔到<br />\n<br />\n幾個鐘人潮"},{"pid":"3f3a840e6dce43d4ce24064a042aef492ca81cb2","tid":1271334,"uid":55168,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T06:12:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山 各自努力 <br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰</span></span>"},{"pid":"505edc3e295400e10dc4748c71744973b6fa9633","tid":1271334,"uid":50457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3f3a840e6dce43d4ce24064a042aef492ca81cb2","tid":1271334,"uid":55168,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T06:12:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山 各自努力 <br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T06:13:57.000Z","msg":"永不放棄"},{"pid":"605d7a6e97d50e2ca9917e82c832e453026d2adb","tid":1271334,"uid":64337,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T06:15:29.000Z","msg":"遊行延期 有咩意義 警犬應該成個機構去做下智力測試<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eee52f4c006db1df2954b002bf2da7614278526","tid":1271334,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"